<HEAD>With LaserPhoto</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By BRENT LAYMON</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>STRATFORD, Conn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
